  <sect3 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Tali</title>

    <para>
      <application>tali</application> is a sort of poker with dice 
      and less money. You roll five dice three times and try to create 
      the best “hand”. Your two rerolls may include any or all of your dice. 
    </para>

    &lfs76_checked;

